<body id="body">
    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>
        <section class="section-base">
            <img id="logovt" class="animate__animated animate__backInRight logo" src="/img/helmet-dark.png" alt="logo">
            <hr class="animate__animated animate__backInRight animate__delay-1s">
            <h5 class="animate__animated animate__bounceIn animate__delay-2s">Official website. Tracker made
                for Assetto Corsa Competizione</h5>
            <h5 class="animate__animated animate__bounceIn animate__delay-2s">Created by Mattia Devigus</h5>
            <div id="arrowCont">
                <a href="#2">
                    <div class="arrow">
                        <span></span>
                        <span></span>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
        <hr>
        <a name="2"></a>
        <section class="section-base">
            <div class="titleCont">
                <h1>What is Vtracker?</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="container-1">
                <div class="row">
                    <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="col col-lg-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-flag-checkered fa-3x"></i>
                        <hr>
                        <p>The vtracker was created mainly to act as a tracker. This software is inspired by the very
                            famous
                            trackers used on AC (see Stracker). The only difference? All of this was done on ACC</p>
                    </div>
                    <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="col col-lg-4">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-3"></div>
                            <div class="col-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-server fa-3x"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-arrow-right fa-3x"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-file-alt fa-3x"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-3"></div>
                        </div>
                        <hr>
                        <p>To save session times, the vtracker uses json files created by ACC servers. For more info
                            consult
                            <a target="_blank"
                                href="https://www.acc-wiki.info/wiki/Server_Configuration#Result_Files">https://www.acc-wiki.info/wiki/Server_Configuration#Result_Files</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300" class="col col-lg-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-lock fa-3x"></i>
                        <hr>
                        <p>The vtracker is also provided with a private area where admins can configure what they need
                            for
                            their use</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <hr>
        <section class="section-base">
            <div class="titleCont">
                <h1>Screenshots</h1>
            </div>
            <div id="screenshoots" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img src="/img/VT1.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="/img/VT2.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="/img/VT3.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="/img/VT4.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#screenshoots" data-bs-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                </button>
                <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#screenshoots" data-bs-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <hr>
        <section class="section-base">
            <div class="titleCont">
                <h1>Download Links</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="col">
                        <img class="vt_download" src="/img/v_icon.png" alt="logo">
                        <hr>
                        <button data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#download" class="btn btn-vtracker">VTRACKER
                            2.0</button>
                        <button data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#tutorial"
                            class="btn btn-vtracker">TUTORIAL</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <div class="modal fade" id="download" tabindex="-1">
            <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Download</h5>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <i class="fas fa-smile-beam fa-3x animate__animated animate__backInRight text-vtracker"></i>
                        <p>Hey, I'm glad you are downloading the vtracker. The product is free, but if you would like to
                            make a donation to support my work, I'd be very happy :)</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <a target="_blank"
                            href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1E7bxISbGL2UnWISZxL0-VZlkWP-38wKY/view?usp=sharing"><button
                                type="button" class="btn btn-vtracker"><i class="fas fa-download"></i></button></a>
                        <a target="_blank" href="https://paypal.me/mattiadevigus?locale.x=it_IT"><button type="button"
                                class="btn btn-primary">Donate</button></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="modal fade" id="tutorial" tabindex="-1">
            <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Tutorial</h5>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <i class="fas fa-tasks fa-3x animate__animated animate__backInRight text-vtracker"></i>
                        <hr>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Download the Vtracker</li>
                            <li>Extract everything to a folder of your choice</li>
                            <li>Enter the folder and open the "config.js" file</li>
                            <li>Set the port (Default: 3000)
                            <li>Choose your username and password</li>
                            <li>There will be two more settings. The one called "resPath" and the other "openOnStart".
                                In the first one you will simply have to enter the path to the results folder of your
                                server (you can do this later via the GUI if you have difficulty, "//" win, "/" linux).
                                The second is a feature that automatically starts the browser with the vtracker page. It
                                is recommended for Windows</li>
                            <li>Are you ready! Start the runnable and have fun! (If you want to enter the "resPath" via
                                GUI, click on "Private Area" at the top right and log in with the credentials you have
                                set)</li>
                            <li>Problems? My Discord is: <u>MattiVers#6866</u></li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <%- include("partials/footer") %>
